                                          to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     tdo-ric-sel-900.
       tdo-ric-sel-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su tipo conto merce                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rr-tip-ctm           not  = spaces
                     go to tdo-ric-sel-800.
           move      "Manca il tipo conto merce !"
                                          to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     tdo-ric-sel-900.
       tdo-ric-sel-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
